---
const hotmartUrl = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_HOTMART_URL || '#';
---

<section class="relative gradient-hero py-20 md:py-28 px-5 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background glow -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[300px] rounded-full bg-purple-heart/20 blur-[100px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="section-intro mb-5">
      no necesitas saber qué escribir
    </p>

    <h2 class="section-title text-white-glow mb-5">
      Solo necesitas empezar.
    </h2>

    <p class="font-body text-base md:text-lg text-soft-lilac/90 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      Tu journal te espera. Con las <strong class="text-white-glow">preguntas correctas</strong>, la <strong class="text-white-glow">música que te entiende</strong>, y un espacio que es solo tuyo.
    </p>

    <p class="font-heading italic text-base text-soft-lilac/70 mb-6">
      "El amor propio no es un concepto, es un camino que se recorre con pausas, dudas y momentos de verdad."
    </p>

    <!-- Price anchor -->
    <div class="mb-6">
      <span class="font-body text-lg text-soft-lilac/50 line-through">$24.90</span>
      <span class="font-body text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white-glow ml-3">$9.90</span>
      <p class="font-accent text-base text-purple-heart mt-1">Precio especial de lanzamiento</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main CTA -->
    <a
      href={hotmartUrl}
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-block gradient-cta text-white-glow font-body font-bold text-lg px-12 py-5 rounded-2xl glow-purple hover:glow-purple-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer animate-pulse-glow"
    >
      Empieza a escribir hoy
    </a>

    <p class="font-body text-xs text-soft-lilac/50 mt-4">
      Descarga inmediata &middot; PDF digital &middot; 165 páginas &middot; 7 capítulos
    </p>

    <!-- Signature -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <img
        src="/images/firma-purple-heart.png"
        alt="Firma de Purple Heart"
        class="h-10 md:h-12 mx-auto opacity-70"
        loading="lazy"
        onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block'"
      />
      <p class="hidden font-accent text-xl text-purple-heart/60">Purple Heart</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
